## Development

### Requirements

- Python 3.11+
- uv package manager
- Node.js (for MCP servers that require it)

### Development Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/billyjbryant/mcp-foxxy-bridge.git
cd mcp-foxxy-bridge

# Install dependencies
uv sync --dev

# Run tests
uv run pytest

# Run linting
uv run ruff check

# Run type checking
uv run mypy src/

# Run the bridge in development
uv run -m mcp_foxxy_bridge --port 8080
```

### Docker Development

```bash
# Build Docker image
docker build -t mcp-foxxy-bridge .

# Run with Docker
docker run --rm -p 8080:8080 mcp-foxxy-bridge
```

